==Black Arm Gang==
===Talking to Charlie the Tramp===
* '''Charlie the Tramp:''' Spare some change, guv?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|quest=no|Who are you?}}
* {{topt|I'm looking for the Black Arm Gang.}}
** '''Player:''' I'm looking for the Black Arm Gang.
** {{tcond|If asking for the first time:}}
*** '''Charlie the Tramp:''' Funny you should mention that... Rumour has it that they have their headquarters right down this alleyway. Though if I were you, I'd be careful about messing with them...
