===Talking to Katrine===
* '''Player:''' What is this place?
* '''Katrine:''' It's a private business. Can I help you at all?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|I've heard you're the Black Arm Gang.}}
** '''Player:''' I've heard you're the Black Arm Gang.
** '''Katrine:''' Who told you that?
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|I'd rather not reveal my sources.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'd rather not reveal my sources.
*** '''Katrine:''' Hmm... I suppose I can understand that. So, say we were the Black Arm Gang, what would you want with us?
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
*** {{topt|I want to become a member of your gang.}}
**** '''Player:''' I want to become a member of your gang.
**** {{tact|Continues after "How unusual..."}}
*** {{topt|I want some hints on becoming a thief.}}
**** '''Player:''' I want some hints on becoming a thief.
**** '''Katrine:''' Do you now? And what makes you think I'll provide anything like that?
**** '''Player:''' Well, how about I become a member of your gang in return?
**** '''Katrine:''' How unusual... Okay, let's say we are who you believe we are. Do you think we'd be recruiting people who just waltz in here saying 'hello, I'd like to play'?
**** '''Player:''' I don't know. What would be the alternative?
**** '''Katrine:''' Watching local thugs and thieves in action, perhaps? How do I know I can just trust someone who's wandered in here.
**** {{tselect|Select an option}}
**** {{topt|Well, you can give me a try can't you?}}
**** '''Player:''' Well, you can give me a try can't you?
**** '''Katrine:''' I'm not so sure...
**** {{tact|Continues below from "Thinking about it..."}}
**** {{topt|Well, people tell me I have an honest face.}}
***** '''Player:''' Well, people tell me I have an honest face.
***** '''Katrine:''' Someone honest wanting to join a gang of thieves? Excuse me if I remain unconvinced...
***** '''Katrine:''' Thinking about it... I may have a solution actually. You may have heard of the Phoenix Gang. I hear they have a very nice weapons stash not too far from here.
***** '''Katrine:''' We're fresh out of crossbows, but apparently they have plenty. If someone were to aquire{{sic}} a couple for us, it would be very much appreciated.
***** '''Player:''' Sounds simple enough. Any particular reason you need them?
***** '''Katrine:''' Let's just say there's a local merchant who is refusing to pay some very reasonable 'keep-your-life-pleasant' insurance rates.
***** '''Player:''' So you're planning to murder him?
***** '''Katrine:''' Him? No. However, I hear that the local law might soon be finding a crossbow belonging to the Phoenix Gang in his home...
***** '''Katrine:''' I also hear that a similar type of crossbow might soon be used in a murder on the other side of the city...
***** '''Katrine:''' Now, are you going to keep asking questions, or are you going to go get those crossbows?
***** {{topt|Okay, no problem.}}
****** '''Player:''' Okay, no problem.
****** '''Katrine:''' Great! Apparently the Phoenix Gang's weapons stash is somewhere to the east. Ask that tramp outside. I'm sure he'll know more.
****** {{tact|end}}
***** {{topt|Sounds a little tricky. Got anything easier?}}
****** '''Player:''' Sounds a little tricky. Got anything easier?
****** '''Katrine:''' If you're not up for a little bit of danger, I don't think you've got anything to offer us.
****** {{tselect|Select an option}}
****** {{topt|Okay, I'll do it.}}
******* '''Player:''' Okay, I'll do it.
******* '''Katrine:''' Great! Apparently the Phoenix Gang's weapons stash is somewhere to the east. Ask that tramp outside. I'm sure he'll know more.
******* {{tact|end}}
****** {{topt|It's a no from me then.}}
******* '''Player:''' It's a no from me then.
******* '''Katrine:''' Then get lost!
******* {{tact|end}}
*** {{topt|I'm looking for the door out of here.}}
**** '''Player:''' I'm looking for the door out of here.
**** '''Katrine:''' Try... the one you just came through?
**** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|It was Charlie, the tramp outside.}}
*** '''Player:''' It was Charlie, the tramp outside.
*** '''Katrine:''' Is that guy still out there? He's getting to be a nuisance. Might be time for him to have a little accident...
*** '''Katrine:''' Anyway, say we were the Black Arm Gang, what would you want with us?
*** {{tact|Continues above after "Say we were the Black Arm Gang, what would you want with us?"}} 
** {{topt|Everyone knows. It's no great secret.}}
*** '''Player:''' Everyone knows. It's no great secret.
*** '''Katrine:''' What?! You must be joking!
*** '''Player:''' Oh no, not at all... It's so obvious! Even the town guard have caught on...
*** '''Katrine:''' I see... Well... say we were the Black Arm Gang, what would you want with us?
*** {{tact|Continues above after "Say we were the Black Arm Gang, what would you want with us?"}} 
* {{topt|What sort of business?}}
** '''Player:''' What sort of business?
** '''Katrine:''' A small, family business. We give financial advice to other companies. Now, if you'll excuse me.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|I'm looking for fame and riches.}}
** '''Player:''' I'm looking for fame and riches.
** '''Katrine:''' And you expect to find that up the back streets of Varrock? Keep dreaming.
** {{tact|end}}

