===Talking to Straven or attempting to open the door===
* '''Player:''' What's through that door?
* '''Straven:''' You can't go in there. Only authorised personnel of the VTAM Corporation are allowed beyond this point.
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|I know who you are!}}
** '''Player:''' I know who you are!
** '''Straven:''' Really? Well? Who are we then?
** '''Player:''' This is the headquarters of one of the most dangerous crime syndicates this city has ever seen! The Phoenix Gang!
** '''Straven:''' No, this is a legitimate business run by legitimate individuals. However... supposing we were this crime gang, what would you want with us?
** {{tselect|Select an option}}
** {{topt|I'd like to offer you my services.}}
