*** '''Straven:''' You mean you'd like to join the Phoenix Gang? Well, obviously I can't speak for them, but the Phoenix Gang doesn't let people join just like that. First, you'd need to prove your loyalty.
*** '''Player:''' How would I go about doing that?
*** '''Straven:''' Obviously, I would have no idea. Although, having said that, a rival gang of ours, er, theirs, called the Black Arm Gang is supposedly meeting a contact from Port Sarim today.
*** '''Straven:''' Apparently the meeting is going to take place in the Blue Moon Inn, and supposedly the contact is none other than the notorious mass murderer turned pirate captain, Jonny the Beard.
*** '''Straven:''' Now, obviously I know nothing about the dealings of the Phoenix Gang, but I bet if somebody were to arrange an accident for Jonny and bring back his intelligence report, the gang would be very pleased.
*** '''Player:''' I see... I'm sure I can help sort something out for them. I'll get right on it.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|I want nothing. I was just making sure you were them.}}
*** '''Player:''' I want nothing. I was just making sure you were them.
*** '''Straven:''' Well then get lost and stop wasting my time.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|How do I get a job with the VTAM corporation?}}
