===Talking to Straven after joining the Phoenix Gang===
* '''Straven:''' Greetings, fellow gang member.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|I've heard you've got some cool treasures in this place.}}
** '''Player:''' I've heard you've got some cool treasures in this place.
** '''Straven:''' Oh yeah, we've all stolen some stuff in our time. Our candlesticks down here, for example, were quite a challenge to get out of the palace.
** '''Player:''' And the Shield of Arrav?
** '''Straven:''' Woah... that's a blast from the past! We stole that years and years ago!
** '''Straven:''' Truth be told, we don't even have the whole shield anymore. A few years ago there was a big fight within the gang and the shield got broken in half as a result.
** '''Straven:''' After the fight, some gang members split off and formed their own group. They took one half of the shield with them.
** '''Player:''' This other group? The Black Arm Gang?
** '''Straven:''' Indeed.
** {{tact|other}}
* {{topt|Any suggestions for where I can go thieving?}}
** '''Player:''' Any suggestions for where I can go thieving?
** '''Straven:''' You could always try the marketplace over in Ardougne. Lots of opportunity there!
** {{tact|other}}
* {{topt|Where's the Black Arm Gang hideout?}}
** '''Player:''' Where's the Black Arm Gang hideout?
** '''Straven:''' Interested in spying on the enemy, are you? It will be tricky. Their security is pretty good. Not as good as ours obviously, but still good.
** '''Straven:''' Still, if you really want to go there, it's down an alleyway near the southern gate. One of our contacts, a tramp going by the name of Charlie, keeps an eye on it. He may be able to help you.
** '''Player:''' I see. Thanks for the help!
** {{tact|other}}
* {{topt|I'd better get going.}}
** '''Player:''' I'd better get going.
** {{tact|end}}

